text: Estadio Municipal de Lo Barnechea is a stadium in Lo Barnechea, Santiago. It's Barnechea's home stadium. The stadium holds 2,500 people. The first football match played in the played in the stadium was a 0–0 draw between Barnechea and Deportes Iberia. ==References== Category:Sports venues in Santiago M
title: Estadio Municipal de Lo Barnechea
